Fonts bundled in this directory (subset .woff2 files, named htf_*.woff2):

- Open Sans — Apache License 2.0
  https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Open+Sans
  (full Apache-2.0 text: ../cyberchef/LICENSE, or https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0)

- Source Code Pro — SIL Open Font License 1.1
  https://github.com/adobe-fonts/source-code-pro
  Full license text: ./OFL.txt

Both licenses permit redistribution and embedding. The files are static subsets
re-served locally so the app works fully offline.
